# pnpm hoisting — make a few well-known transitive deps visible at root
# node_modules so bundlers (Vite/Rollup) can resolve them without per-app
# config tweaks. Without this, pnpm's strict isolated-tree layout means
# packages like react-remove-scroll (which `import "tslib"`) only succeed
# when their pnpm version happens to link tslib into their own
# .pnpm/<pkg>/node_modules — which varies between pnpm 9.x point releases.
public-hoist-pattern[]=tslib
public-hoist-pattern[]=*types*
